{"tid":1765542,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人真係好撚cheap 同啲偽有錢腥梘人9樣","createTime":"2019-12-02T02:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T12:03:33.000Z","uid":313313,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b66116e8a3b9465e11d293f33667cf7e3549f21f","tid":1765542,"uid":313313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"朋友係某大屋苑小店做 最近得閒就過去玩下<br />\n<br />\n個到啲人真係cheap到一個點<br />\n-<strong>買野要袋唔撚比膠袋錢（$0.5）<br />\n-有時仲問你有冇得平啲<br />\n-傾多幾句就好撚熟咁款，$203就話齊頭唔洗收個$3</strong><br />\n咩料呀 你會唔會係sogo，citysupper 叫個staff 唔收尾數？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到大公司就好撚豪咁款,比tips都唔至比$3啦我估<br />\n<br />\n講到自己唔憤氣，就會鬧鳩你，個幾蚊都要收<br />\n<br />\n真係同大陸人一鳩<br />\n有時仲搵錢搭你添<br />\n<br />\n可能我依啲自係好少事。有冇人有同感？"},{"pid":"1f944153624d42e137cdbe55abb964fff3f80acb","tid":1765542,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"呢個情況係所謂中產尤其多"},{"pid":"0b603a9e25aa3099ebc870ade54eb1a7d3f8a9b9","tid":1765542,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"講價去街市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68c6d24da4d98d26fd85e479f2542c81f835c38","tid":1765542,"uid":313313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b603a9e25aa3099ebc870ade54eb1a7d3f8a9b9","tid":1765542,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"講價去街市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"我諗街市都冇得講 會比人吊柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75422c554123bcaeb62c8152aadccd7f9d1526b0","tid":1765542,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f944153624d42e137cdbe55abb964fff3f80acb","tid":1765542,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"呢個情況係所謂中產尤其多"},"cited